      <title></title>
      <link href="2021/06/03/Modulation%20Envelope%20&amp;%20LFO%E4%BD%8E%E9%A2%91%E6%8C%AF%E8%8D%A1%E5%99%A8/"/>
      <url>2021/06/03/Modulation%20Envelope%20&amp;%20LFO%E4%BD%8E%E9%A2%91%E6%8C%AF%E8%8D%A1%E5%99%A8/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Modulation-Envelope-amp-LFO低频振荡器"><a href="#Modulation-Envelope-amp-LFO低频振荡器" class="headerlink" title="Modulation Envelope &amp; LFO低频振荡器"></a>Modulation Envelope &amp; LFO低频振荡器</h1><p> <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-29_220540.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-29_220540.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p>选项旁边按钮为调变力度，偏向左是负值，右是正值，中间为0值，即无变化。</p><h2 id="LFO"><a href="#LFO" class="headerlink" title="LFO"></a>LFO</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-29_221601.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-29_221601.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p>长这样，Rate为频率，Gain为力度，Offset为强度</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-29_222010.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-29_222010.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p>此灯点亮时，代表合成器内时间包络关联到了DAW中，数值单位一般显示为小节拍数，关闭后变为Hz</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title></title>
      <link href="2021/06/03/MISC%20Modulation/"/>
      <url>2021/06/03/MISC%20Modulation/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="MISC-Modulation-amp-Keyboard-Section"><a href="#MISC-Modulation-amp-Keyboard-Section" class="headerlink" title="MISC Modulation &amp; Keyboard Section"></a>MISC Modulation &amp; Keyboard Section</h1><h2 id="MISC"><a href="#MISC" class="headerlink" title="MISC"></a>MISC</h2><h3 id="source"><a href="#source" class="headerlink" title="source"></a>source</h3><p>velocity——按keyboard力度</p><p>mod wheel——keyboard旁滚轮</p><p>keytrack——音阶</p><p>aftertouch——keyboard功能 保持按压下的二次按压</p><h5 id="STEP"><a href="#STEP" class="headerlink" title="STEP"></a>STEP</h5><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-06-02_232041.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-06-02_232041.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><h2 id="Keyboard-Section"><a href="#Keyboard-Section" class="headerlink" title="Keyboard Section"></a>Keyboard Section</h2><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-06-03_145453.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-06-03_145453.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p>左侧滚轮为<strong>Bend Range</strong> 右侧滚轮为<strong>Mod Wheel</strong></p><h4 id="Bend-Range"><a href="#Bend-Range" class="headerlink" title="Bend Range"></a>Bend Range</h4><p>在弹奏midi键盘时，滚动可以改变音高，<strong>12单位的Band Range = 一个八度音</strong>。</p><h4 id="Mod-Wheel"><a href="#Mod-Wheel" class="headerlink" title="Mod Wheel"></a>Mod Wheel</h4><p>可以作为MISC中的Source进行调变。</p><h4 id="MONO-Legato"><a href="#MONO-Legato" class="headerlink" title="MONO Legato"></a>MONO Legato</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-06-03_145827.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-06-03_145827.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p>开启后，Sylenth1强制进入单音模式。</p><h4 id="Portamento"><a href="#Portamento" class="headerlink" title="Portamento"></a>Portamento</h4><p>滑音，转动可以改变滑音的量。</p><h4 id="N-S-（Normal-Slide模式）"><a href="#N-S-（Normal-Slide模式）" class="headerlink" title="N/S （Normal / Slide模式）"></a>N/S （Normal / Slide模式）</h4><p>Normal模式下，需持续按住前一个音符才会产生滑音效果，Slide模式下单音间过渡即可产生滑音效果。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title></title>
      <link href="2021/06/03/Filter%20&amp;%20Filter%20Control%20%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8&amp;%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6/"/>
      <url>2021/06/03/Filter%20&amp;%20Filter%20Control%20%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8&amp;%E6%BB%A4%E6%B3%A2%E5%99%A8%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Filter-amp-Filter-Control-滤波器-amp-滤波器控制"><a href="#Filter-amp-Filter-Control-滤波器-amp-滤波器控制" class="headerlink" title="Filter &amp; Filter Control 滤波器&amp;滤波器控制"></a>Filter &amp; Filter Control 滤波器&amp;滤波器控制</h1><h2 id="Filter"><a href="#Filter" class="headerlink" title="Filter"></a>Filter</h2><p>每台osc都对应了一台Filter，以Filter A为例，在input select处可以选择上层输入源</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-28_232023.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-28_232023.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p>如图，可设定源为osc A 、osc A&amp;B以及No input</p><p>Filter Type处可选择不同滤波类型：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-28_232433.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-28_232433.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p>Bypass——不对经过Filter的声音进行改变，直接输送到AMP ENV</p><p>Lowpass——低频可通过，过滤高频</p><p>Bandpass——通过指定Cutoff值来确定截值点</p><p>Highpass——与Lowpass相反</p><p>Resonance——负责控制Cutoff的频率（共鸣数值）</p><p>Drive——设定Filter过载值</p><h2 id="Filter-Control"><a href="#Filter-Control" class="headerlink" title="Filter Control"></a>Filter Control</h2><p>可同时控制Filter A&amp;B</p><p>Key Track——控制midi键盘弹奏的音阶对Filter的影响</p><p>Warm Drive——开启后会让Filter产生更多泛音</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title></title>
      <link href="2021/05/28/Retrig%20Phrase%20&amp;%20Inv/"/>
      <url>2021/05/28/Retrig%20Phrase%20&amp;%20Inv/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Retrig-Phrase-amp-Inv"><a href="#Retrig-Phrase-amp-Inv" class="headerlink" title="Retrig Phrase &amp; Inv"></a>Retrig Phrase &amp; Inv</h1><p>位于oscillator部分的以下三个位置</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-28_142759.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-28_142759.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p>需要 2+ 个oscillator开启后生效</p><h2 id="Phrase"><a href="#Phrase" class="headerlink" title="Phrase"></a>Phrase</h2><p>更改 wavefrom 的起始点，需要搭配 Retrig 按钮开启使用</p><p>范围（0 ， 360）</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-28_143307.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-28_143307.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><h2 id="Retrig"><a href="#Retrig" class="headerlink" title="Retrig"></a>Retrig</h2><p>开启后，固定 wavefrom 的起始位置在同一个点。</p><p>如果关闭，则起始位置为随机点，同时 Phrase 设定不生效。</p><h2 id="Inv"><a href="#Inv" class="headerlink" title="Inv"></a>Inv</h2><p>相位翻转，将发声波形水平翻转。</p><p>如果在同一个osc中使用同波形，默认都开启Retrig，一台开启Inv，一台不开启，则声波互相抵消，表现为不发声。</p><p>同理，使用不同波形，则表现为合成波形。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title></title>
      <link href="2021/05/27/Voice%20&amp;%20OSC%20%E5%A3%B0%E9%9F%B3%E4%B8%8E%E6%8C%AF%E8%8D%A1%E5%99%A8/"/>
      <url>2021/05/27/Voice%20&amp;%20OSC%20%E5%A3%B0%E9%9F%B3%E4%B8%8E%E6%8C%AF%E8%8D%A1%E5%99%A8/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Voice-amp-OSC-声音与振荡器"><a href="#Voice-amp-OSC-声音与振荡器" class="headerlink" title="Voice &amp; OSC 声音与振荡器"></a>Voice &amp; OSC 声音与振荡器</h1><p>OSC在Sylenth1中体现为Part A和Part B两部分，每个Part面板都包含独属的osclllator、AMP ENV、Filter等部分。</p><h2 id="OSC参数"><a href="#OSC参数" class="headerlink" title="OSC参数"></a>OSC参数</h2><h3 id="发声数"><a href="#发声数" class="headerlink" title="发声数"></a>发声数</h3><p>Sylenth1是一台Polyphony合成器（多音合成器） </p><p>左上角的Polyphony数值控制着midi键盘同时按下的键位数</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-27_213636.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-27_213636.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p>右侧的Voices数代表着最大发声数，分子为实时发声数，分母为期望发声数。分母由osclllator面板上Voices数乘以Polyphony数值得出，最大数值为512。</p><h3 id="Pitch"><a href="#Pitch" class="headerlink" title="Pitch"></a>Pitch</h3><p>osclllator面板上的Pitch由三部分组成：</p><p> <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-27_214217.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-27_214217.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p>Octave——八度音</p><p>范围（ -3 ，+3）</p><p>Note—— 半音</p><p>范围（-7 ， +7）</p><p>Fine——半音内</p><p>范围（-1 ， +1）</p><p>在调节面板上，仅显示旋钮，不显示具体数值，查看具体数值需要将鼠标停滞于旋钮上，名称与数值会显示在屏幕中央面板处。</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-27_214739.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-27_214739.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p>需要进行微调时，按住键盘的Shift键进行调节。</p><h3 id="Volume"><a href="#Volume" class="headerlink" title="Volume"></a>Volume</h3><p>控制声音响度</p><h3 id="Wave"><a href="#Wave" class="headerlink" title="Wave"></a>Wave</h3><p>sylenth1合成器共内置如下种波形：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-27_215054.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-27_215054.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p>其中Noise为全频噪音。</p><h3 id="Detune"><a href="#Detune" class="headerlink" title="Detune"></a>Detune</h3><p>在Voices数目＞1时可用，调节声音的厚度。</p><h3 id="Stereo"><a href="#Stereo" class="headerlink" title="Stereo"></a>Stereo</h3><p>控制立体声道的宽广程度，范围（0 ， 10），0为单声道，10为立体声。</p><h3 id="Pan"><a href="#Pan" class="headerlink" title="Pan"></a>Pan</h3><p>控制由左至右坐标轴上的声像，范围（-10 ， 10），分别对应左右声道。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title></title>
      <link href="2021/05/26/Sylenth1%E5%90%88%E6%88%90%E5%99%A8/"/>
      <url>2021/05/26/Sylenth1%E5%90%88%E6%88%90%E5%99%A8/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Sylenth1合成器"><a href="#Sylenth1合成器" class="headerlink" title="Sylenth1合成器"></a>Sylenth1合成器</h1><h3 id="一、声音走向"><a href="#一、声音走向" class="headerlink" title="一、声音走向"></a>一、声音走向</h3><p>​    合成器共包含4个Oscillator（振荡器），Part A/B 各两个。</p><p>​    采用层级结构如下图：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-23_221724.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-23_221724.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p>其中，声音输出前的Master Effects居于效果器中央，共有以下</p><p><strong>Distort——琶音</strong></p><p><strong>Phaser——失真</strong></p><p><strong>Chorus——相位</strong></p><p><strong>EQ</strong></p><p><strong>Delay——延音</strong></p><p><strong>Reverb——混响</strong></p><p><strong>Compress——压缩</strong> </p><p>以及一个midi效果器：<strong>ARPEG</strong> </p><h3 id="二、使用Preset"><a href="#二、使用Preset" class="headerlink" title="二、使用Preset"></a>二、使用Preset</h3><p>​    在menu主选项卡下，包含对Preset的设置与所在的Bank列表，一个Bank中最多有512个Preset</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-23_222739.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-23_222739.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><p>​    Preset选项卡下，可以载入本地Preset、保存选定的Preset等，其中，Clear是清空选定Preset的所    有设置，Reset是将Preset恢复为上一次保存的状态。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>AMP ENV &amp; Mixer</title>
      <link href="2021/04/20/AMP%20ENV%20&amp;%20Mixer/"/>
      <url>2021/04/20/AMP%20ENV%20&amp;%20Mixer/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="AMP-ENV-amp-Mixer"><a href="#AMP-ENV-amp-Mixer" class="headerlink" title="AMP ENV &amp; Mixer"></a>AMP ENV &amp; Mixer</h1><h2 id="AMP-ENV"><a href="#AMP-ENV" class="headerlink" title="AMP ENV"></a>AMP ENV</h2><p>上层为Filter</p><p>通过A D S R控制音量变化</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-28_235441.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amzsowhat/image/img/blog_12021-05-28_235441.png" srcset="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAABGdBTUEAALGPC/xhBQAAADhlWElmTU0AKgAAAAgAAYdpAAQAAAABAAAAGgAAAAAAAqACAAQAAAABAAAAAaADAAQAAAABAAAAAQAAAADa6r/EAAAAC0lEQVQIHWNgAAIAAAUAAY27m/MAAAAASUVORK5CYII="></p><ul><li><h4 id="Attack-起音"><a href="#Attack-起音" class="headerlink" title="Attack 起音"></a>Attack 起音</h4><p><strong>Attack参数分为Attack time（起音时间）和Attack Level（起音音量）</strong></p><p>​    Attack time越大，代表该音色从发声到音量最大之间的时间越长，有渐进感</p><p>​    值越小，则该时间越短，音色越铿锵。</p><p>​    Attack Level决定了该音色达到的最大音量数值。</p></li><li><h4 id="Decay-衰减"><a href="#Decay-衰减" class="headerlink" title="Decay 衰减"></a>Decay 衰减</h4><p><strong>Decay参数分为Decay time（衰减时间）和Decay Level（衰减音量）</strong></p><p>​    音色达到最大音量后，衰减至稳定音量，Decay Time决定该过程的速度。</p></li><li><h4 id="Sustain-维持"><a href="#Sustain-维持" class="headerlink" title="Sustain 维持"></a>Sustain 维持</h4><p><strong>Sustain参数只有Sustain Time</strong></p><p>​    音色在经过了Attack和Decay后，会进入到一个稳定的状态，Sustain Time指一直按住midi键盘情况    下，声音可以持续多久。如鼓的音色，Sustain Time较短，钢琴则较长，而对于管弦乐音色，只要一    直按住不放琴键，声音就一直维持，Sustain Time无限大。</p></li><li><h4 id="Release-释放"><a href="#Release-释放" class="headerlink" title="Release 释放"></a>Release 释放</h4><p><strong>Release参数也只有Release Time</strong></p><p>​    指停止弹奏（放开琴键）后，声音维持的时间</p></li></ul><p>在设计音色时，可以先对音色的曲线进行大致构思。</p><h2 id="Mixer"><a href="#Mixer" class="headerlink" title="Mixer"></a>Mixer</h2><p>通过三个推子调整Part A、B和整体的音量。</p><p>控制音量表在绿色范围内防止爆音。</p>]]></content>
      
      
